514, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999777323019777, \"rank\": 2.226819383069994e-05, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They have been virtually invincible since and, in the last ever lightweight double sculls race at theOlympicsbefore it is removed from the rowing schedule, they lived up to their billing as arguably the world's best crew across all the disciplines.\", \"from\": 517, \"to\": 765, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They were the sport's global crew of the year in 2023 and had arrived in Paris unbeaten in 11 regattas.\", \"from\": 767, \"to\": 870, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 840, \"end\": 845, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999777323019777, \"rank\": 2.226819383069994e-05, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As a pair, they have become incredibly in tune, to the extent they turned up at last year's World Championships reading the exact same book.\", \"from\": 871, \"to\": 1011, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In Friday's race, they fell behind the Romanians early on, the first time this season they have been properly under pressure.\", \"from\": 1013, \"to\": 1138, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1052, \"end\": 1061, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanians\", \"score\": 0.994788219005582, \"rank\": 0.005218695298406446, \"text\": \"Romanians\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biding their time, they waited until the third quarter of the race to put the hammer down and, by 500metres, they had pulled out a lead of a boat's length.\", \"from\": 1140, \"to\": 1295, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\